    Modifier and Type
    Class
    Description
    class 
    VmSchedulerSpaceShared
    VmSchedulerSpaceShared is a VMM allocation policy that allocates one or more PEs from a host to a Virtual Machine Monitor (VMM), and doesn't allow sharing of PEs.
    class 
    VmSchedulerTimeShared
    VmSchedulerTimeShared is a Virtual Machine Monitor (VMM) allocation policy that allocates one or more PEs from a PM to a VM, and allows sharing of PEs by multiple VMs.
    class 
    VmSchedulerTimeSharedOverSubscription
    This is a Time-Shared VM Scheduler, which allows over-subscription.
